docs {
  # Workspace Invitations

  Endpoints for managing workspace user invitations.

  - **Send Invitation**: Owner can invite a named pharmacist and set their default password (authenticated, owner role required)
  - **Accept Invitation**: Accept an invitation and create the pharmacist account. The pharmacist then signs in with the default password and must change it before workspace access.
}
